# Oktyabrsky, Republic of Adygea

}}
Oktyabrsky (; ) is a rural locality (a khutor) in Kirovskoye Rural Settlement of Maykopsky District, Russia. The population was 52 as of 2018. There are 2 streets.
Geography
Oktyabrsky is located 21 km north of Tulsky (the district's administrative centre) by road. Grozny is the nearest rural locality.
